# 📑 Hotfix 04/22/2025 - 04/XX/2025

## 🟢 Status `Released`

## 💬 Patch Notes

________

## 📢 Features and Improvements

### 🔼 `Improvement` Improved prone animation.
- Character arms no longer move up and down with where the player is looking.

________

## 🐛 Bugfixes
- Fixed a bug which allowed players to jump while sitting in cars.
- Fixed a bug which caused the wrong weapon to be selected after exiting a car or ladder.
- Fixed a bug which prevented players from seeing their squad chat after rejoining.
- Fixed a bug where some containers didn't have any slots (tents, typically).
- Fixed a bug where the MP-133 had a visible shotgun shell floating in the air.
- [CONTROLLER] Fixed a bug which prevented controller keybinds from loading.
- [CONTROLLER] Fixed a bug which prevented controllers from using the radial menu in some cases (pinging, locking doors, etc).

- Fixed a **major** bug which prevented players from interacting, moving items, pinging, etc.
